      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm working on a UI for a new banking app. we want the vibe to be really calm and professional. the main brand color is a deep navy blue (hex #000080). can you suggest some complementary and analogous colors that would work well for a high-end corporate look? maybe some specific hex codes too.",
